ActCanada Mortgage and Housing Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Minister Housing and Diversity and Inclusion of ANDRÉ HÉBERT of Longueuil, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation, to hold office during pleasure, on a part-time basis, for a term of two years, effective February 27, 2023.
